到第一段说的，好像我跟他用的不是一个系统似的。</p>\n<p>我用下来觉得小米最多广告而且无法避免的就是应用商店。然后可能是小米钱包这种金融类的 app ，就小米钱包来说，绑定了银行卡后就只剩下双击电源呼出 mipay 支付了，很少再去打开 app 的。而 mipay 界面是只有选择银行卡没有广告的。</p>\n<p>其他官方提供的小工具经过设置，可以说几乎没怎么感觉到有广告（广告彻底关闭了或者广告存在感很低或者是一次设置完就不用再打开的）。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1680620410, "replies": 100, "id": 929862}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 4176, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1096, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 559267, "username": "MMMing", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/MMMing", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a2f87f2c29db5edf6ad945034ee506e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a2f87f2c29db5edf6ad945034ee506e?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a2f87f2c29db5edf6ad945034ee506e?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1634809350, "last_modified": 1634809350}, "last_reply_by": "dilibaba", "last_touched": 1680679921, "title": "高房租下的奇怪金钱观", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/929820", "created": 1680607809, "deleted": 0, "content": "买个 7 ，8 百的机械键盘要犹豫好久\r\n每个月 4 ，5 千的房租 交起来心无波澜", "content_rendered": "<p>买个 7 ，8 百的机械键盘要犹豫好久\n每个月 4 ，5 千的房租 交起来心无波澜</p>\n", "last_modified": 1680607809, "replies": 55, "id": 929820}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 200730, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。